title: CLASSIC XXX - Kelly O'Dell - Sensual Exposure (1993)
description:
Kelly O'Dell masturbates her way through a number of vignettes, learning about the Art of Love as she goes.

At first, the narrative argument of the movie sounds common as the 100th sequel of the same stupid story : a man wants his bride to be a perfect lover and wants her to teach sex in a strange and luxury college. But after a few seconds, it is clear that story has no importance at all and that we are entering, step by step with the narrative Kelly ODell, into a kind of Wonderland. It could be ridiculous but it is not. Andrew Blake pictures are so beautiful that actors and actresses are almost contemplative of their own beauties, as we are... No vulgarity but freedom ; no useless words but mere music ; no intellectual meaning but pure sensitive beauty. This movie as the same effect, after it is finished, as the glitterings of a very beautiful erotic dream...
